<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb7d92001-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea" identifier="/us/usc/t5/s805"><num value="805">§ 805.</num><heading> Judicial review</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">No determination, finding, action, or omission under this chapter shall be subject to judicial review.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb7d92002-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/104/121/tII/s251">Pub. L. 104–121, title II, § 251</ref>, <date date="1996-03-29">Mar. 29, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/873">110 Stat. 873</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
